Scotty Mattraw https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Scotty_Mattraw 0 Winfield Scott "Scotty" Mattraw (October 19, 1880 – November 9, 1946) was an American film and television actor. Mattraw provided the voice of Bashful in Walt Disney's Snow White and the Seven Dwarfs.
